' Bonus probe for commands/functions found in binaries but absent from core.json 
' From missing_offsets.txt BONUS section 
On Error Goto _ERR
Follow 
Follow Off 
Screen Open 0,320,200,16,Lowres
Get Cblock 1,0,0,16,16
Put Cblock 1
Put Cblock 1,10,10
Del Cblock 
Del Cblock 1
P=Port(1)
PN$=Prg Next$
Print P,D,PF$,PN$,PS$
End 
_ERR:
Resume Next 
